          |     &lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="dropdown-item" href="#"&gt;Separated link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
          |   &lt;/ul&gt;
          | &lt;/div&gt;

      h4 Sizing
      p Button dropdowns work with buttons of all sizes, including default and split dropdown buttons.

      .bd-example
