      h4 Directions

      h4 Centered
      p Make the dropdown menu centered below the toggle with <code>.dropdown-center</code> on the parent element.

      .bd-example
        .dropdown-center
          button.btn.btn-secondary.dropdown-toggle(type='button' data-bs-toggle='dropdown' aria-expanded='false')
            | Centered dropdown
          ul.dropdown-menu
            li
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Action
            li
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Action two
            li
              a.dropdown-item(href='#') Action three

